## General info
This Project is a simple API for keeping statistics about board game plays and board games itself. 

## Technologies
Project contains:
* Java version: 11
* Spring Boot version: 2.6.4
* Swagger version: 2.9.2
* Lombok
* Spring Web
* MS SQL Server Driver
* Spring Data JPA

